InorigoJS

Get Started →

Simple API

The API for InorigoJS is super simple to understand, even for the novice. You will be up and running in just one minute.

Powerful features

With InorigoJS you are able to interact with Inorigo in some really cool ways. The sky's the limit!

Familiarity

InorigoJS is built using Axios, and anyone familiar with Axios will be able to understand the output from the API functions.
